## §2 · Read processing and quantification

Raw sequencing data were processed by **[sequencing provider]** using the 
Illumina DRAGEN RNA pipeline (v**[version]**). DRAGEN performed read 
filtering, alignment to the *Rattus norvegicus* rn7 reference genome 
(Ensembl release **[version]**), and gene-level quantification via its 
integrated Salmon implementation. Gene-level quantification files 
(`quant.genes.sf`) were imported into R using tximport (v1.40.0).

