- apeglm shrinkage: Zhu A, Ibrahim JG, Love MI (2018) *Bioinformatics* 34:2084–2092
- Wald test / BH correction: Benjamini Y, Hochberg Y (1995) *J R Stat Soc B* 57:289–300
